1
00:01:36,388 --> 00:01:38,390
How long you gonna be?.

2
00:01:47,316 --> 00:01:48,483
Be right out,

3
00:01:49,526 --> 00:01:51,486
you're a pain!

4
00:02:17,387 --> 00:02:18,388
Hey, American.

5
00:02:18,472 --> 00:02:20,432
I'm still here, gettin' a manicure.

6
00:02:21,517 --> 00:02:24,478
Things okay?.

7
00:02:25,312 --> 00:02:27,439
Gettin' tanned?. Don't get burned!

8
00:02:28,440 --> 00:02:30,317
Bruno's here too.

9
00:02:30,400 --> 00:02:32,402
You got a crap body!

10
00:02:33,529 --> 00:02:35,531
Is Bruno here?.

11
00:02:36,365 --> 00:02:37,449
He's over there.

12
00:02:44,456 --> 00:02:46,458
You doin' a lamp?.

13
00:03:53,317 --> 00:03:54,401
It's 2,000.

14
00:03:54,484 --> 00:03:57,362
How much are you
supposed to get this week?.

15
00:03:57,446 --> 00:03:58,530
9,200.

16
00:03:59,364 --> 00:04:02,326
Sure?. It was less last week.

17
00:04:03,410 --> 00:04:05,370
Yes, Don Ciro 9,200.

18
00:04:07,331 --> 00:04:09,374
Another 2,000 euro and we're even.

19
00:04:10,375 --> 00:04:12,336
Don Ciro, don't take all day.

20
00:04:12,419 --> 00:04:14,296
He's slow.

21
00:04:15,380 --> 00:04:17,424
Hurry, so we can go home.

22
00:04:19,384 --> 00:04:21,345
Things okay out there?.

23
00:04:21,428 --> 00:04:22,554
Keep your eyes open.

24
00:04:33,357 --> 00:04:34,483
That's it.

25
00:04:39,488 --> 00:04:41,448
Put paper cups in.

26
00:04:46,328 --> 00:04:47,538
Toilet paper.

27
00:04:54,419 --> 00:04:57,297
- Then, Mom?.
- Some shampoo.

28
00:04:59,383 --> 00:05:00,509
A mozzarella...

29
00:05:05,347 --> 00:05:07,391
Shampoo, not bath oil!

30
00:05:07,516 --> 00:05:10,352
You're rushin' me!

31
00:05:10,435 --> 00:05:12,437
And you're drivin' me crazy!

32
00:05:17,359 --> 00:05:20,320
Hurry up, there are
more groceries to deliver.

33
00:05:20,404 --> 00:05:22,322
- Nothing else?.
- No.

34
00:05:26,493 --> 00:05:29,454
- Be back later.
- Don't get yourself lost.

35
00:05:40,507 --> 00:05:42,551
- Simone.
- Toto, what's up?.

36
00:05:43,385 --> 00:05:46,346
- What's happening?.
- I'm workin'.

37
00:05:47,514 --> 00:05:50,517
Know what happened?.
They arrested Vitale and Bon Bon.

38
00:05:51,310 --> 00:05:52,394
Really?.

39
00:05:52,477 --> 00:05:55,480
- Got somethin' to eat?.
- Yeah, but it's not mine.

40
00:05:55,564 --> 00:05:57,441
Bye, see you.

41
00:06:13,499 --> 00:06:15,375
Carmela, ma'am!

42
00:06:21,423 --> 00:06:22,549
Hi, Boxer.

43
00:06:49,409 --> 00:06:51,370
Two doses, two doses!

44
00:06:52,371 --> 00:06:54,373
Please, give me a dose!

45
00:06:59,419 --> 00:07:01,338
Gaetano, check it!

46
00:07:34,371 --> 00:07:36,331
One, two, three...

47
00:07:40,460 --> 00:07:41,503
Goodbye.

48
00:07:43,547 --> 00:07:45,507
Don Ciro, be more punctual.

49
00:07:46,425 --> 00:07:48,343
I'll pass it on.

50
00:07:56,351 --> 00:07:57,436
Eleven and twelve.

51
00:07:58,353 --> 00:08:00,355
See if he wants coffee.

52
00:08:00,439 --> 00:08:02,441
No, but thank you anyway....

53
00:08:02,524 --> 00:08:04,401
I'll show you out.

54
00:08:04,526 --> 00:08:06,361
Have a good day.

55
00:08:14,578 --> 00:08:16,371
Four hundred...

56
00:08:20,501 --> 00:08:21,543
Five hundred.

57
00:08:22,377 --> 00:08:24,421
The same amount again?.

58
00:08:25,464 --> 00:08:28,425
I've said a hundred times
I can't manage like this.

59
00:08:29,343 --> 00:08:30,427
Don Carlo...

60
00:08:33,472 --> 00:08:37,309
Did you tell them I can't manage
on this chickenfeed?.

61
00:08:37,518 --> 00:08:40,354
I have to pay rent, lights, water.

62
00:08:41,396 --> 00:08:44,316
I can't survive,
I'm strapped with debts.

63
00:08:44,441 --> 00:08:47,444
- I'll pass it on.
- You always say that!

64
00:08:47,486 --> 00:08:50,322
Are you mockin' me?.

65
00:08:51,406 --> 00:08:52,533
I don't get it!

66
00:08:53,325 --> 00:08:54,535
Listen,

67
00:08:55,369 --> 00:08:57,412
I've got a son to support,

68
00:08:57,496 --> 00:09:00,457
for forty years
I've kept him off the streets,

69
00:09:01,458 --> 00:09:03,418
he's unemployed.

70
00:09:03,502 --> 00:09:06,463
What can I do,
go over to the other side?.

71
00:09:07,422 --> 00:09:11,385
They know, I served you honestly
for forty years.

72
00:09:11,426 --> 00:09:14,471
My wife's in jail,
is this the thanks we get?.

73
00:09:15,347 --> 00:09:18,308
Are we crazy?.
Do I have to raise hell?.

74
00:09:21,436 --> 00:09:22,479
Silvana!

75
00:09:30,529 --> 00:09:32,322
May I?.

76
00:09:34,491 --> 00:09:35,576
Come on in!

77
00:09:36,410 --> 00:09:37,411
Maria!

78
00:09:39,538 --> 00:09:41,331
The bill?.

79
00:09:41,415 --> 00:09:43,458
Talk to Mom.

80
00:09:49,590 --> 00:09:51,383
Put this in your pocket.

81
00:09:51,550 --> 00:09:53,385
Thank you.

82
00:10:06,440 --> 00:10:08,400
Carabinieri on the street!

83
00:10:18,535 --> 00:10:20,495
He's comin' out!

84
00:10:38,514 --> 00:10:41,350
I'm the best, number one!

85
00:10:41,433 --> 00:10:42,518
So?.

86
00:10:43,393 --> 00:10:44,436
Go, Marco!

87
00:10:44,520 --> 00:10:48,524
- I'll blast these roaches!
- Who do you think you're fighting?.

88
00:10:49,316 --> 00:10:52,319
I'm number one! Tony Montana!

89
00:10:52,444 --> 00:10:54,446
The world is ours!

90
00:10:54,571 --> 00:10:57,407
You don't know
who you're up against!

91
00:10:57,449 --> 00:10:59,451
I'm Tony Montana!

92
00:10:59,576 --> 00:11:02,371
- I'm the powerhouse!
- Yeah!

93
00:11:02,454 --> 00:11:03,497
Come here.

94
00:11:05,374 --> 00:11:07,376
Shit Colombians,

95
00:11:07,459 --> 00:11:09,378
they're everywhere.

96
00:11:09,545 --> 00:11:12,339
See, Colombians everywhere.

97
00:11:15,592 --> 00:11:18,345
You really looked like Scarface.

98
00:11:28,438 --> 00:11:30,357
You were good.

99
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:32,568
Now it all has to be ours,
the whole world.

100
00:11:33,527 --> 00:11:35,404
Miami, all of it.

101
00:11:49,418 --> 00:11:51,503
My friend, got stuff?.

102
00:12:01,388 --> 00:12:02,556
You got stuff?.

103
00:12:07,561 --> 00:12:10,439
- Got good stuff?.
- You got money?.

104
00:12:10,522 --> 00:12:14,359
- Sure, you got coke?.
- What do you want to pay?.

105
00:12:14,443 --> 00:12:16,486
Me?. 50.

106
00:12:18,363 --> 00:12:21,533
- 55, can you do it?.
- No, 55 is too much, 50.

107
00:12:22,576 --> 00:12:24,536
You sure?.

108
00:12:25,454 --> 00:12:27,372
Wait here for me.

109
00:12:36,423 --> 00:12:37,591
Where's Smarty?.

110
00:12:55,442 --> 00:12:56,485
Hey, kid!

111
00:13:09,414 --> 00:13:11,333
Give him the money.

112
00:13:16,588 --> 00:13:19,424
- Is it all here?.
- Yeah.

113
00:13:34,606 --> 00:13:37,359
- Okay?.
- Yes.

114
00:13:40,529 --> 00:13:43,448
- Want to see it?.
- I want to try it.

115
00:13:45,409 --> 00:13:46,577
I gave you the money!

116
00:13:47,411 --> 00:13:48,495
Wait!

117
00:13:53,584 --> 00:13:55,502
Open your hand.

118
00:13:59,381 --> 00:14:00,424
It's good.

119
00:14:03,385 --> 00:14:04,595
Give me all of it!

120
00:14:13,478 --> 00:14:15,355
Grab the money!

121
00:15:22,381 --> 00:15:24,424
Giovanni, I brought the kids.

122
00:15:24,508 --> 00:15:25,551
Come in.

123
00:15:29,346 --> 00:15:31,557
You know very well why you're here.

124
00:15:32,391 --> 00:15:35,561
Too much ruckus going on in my area,
because I'm the boss here.

125
00:15:36,395 --> 00:15:37,604
That's just you sayin'.

126
00:15:39,398 --> 00:15:41,567
If I had you come here, I know.
No back-talk

127
00:15:42,401 --> 00:15:44,528
or I'll smash your face!

128
00:15:45,445 --> 00:15:48,574
- What happened?.
- For the moment, nothing.

129
00:15:49,491 --> 00:15:50,576
Get me?.

130
00:15:51,410 --> 00:15:55,455
I can't be made to look bad
because of two kids like you.

131
00:15:55,581 --> 00:15:58,542
The next time
I hear anything about you,

132
00:15:59,376 --> 00:16:00,544
I'll blow your heads off.

133
00:16:01,420 --> 00:16:04,381
- If it's like you say...
- Shut up when I'm talking.

134
00:16:04,464 --> 00:16:06,508
Then if I come to realize

135
00:16:07,467 --> 00:16:09,511
you're worth something,

136
00:16:09,595 --> 00:16:12,389
which I'll determine and I'll decide,

137
00:16:12,556 --> 00:16:15,350
you can work for me.

138
00:16:15,517 --> 00:16:17,519
Is that clear?.

139
00:16:18,562 --> 00:16:20,397
Show them out.

140
00:16:26,445 --> 00:16:28,405
"I'll smash your face!"

141
00:16:28,488 --> 00:16:30,532
And I'll tear your beard!

142
00:16:31,450 --> 00:16:33,368
Without a T-shirt.

143
00:16:33,452 --> 00:16:35,496
"Sweet Pea", looked like a bum.

144
00:16:36,538 --> 00:16:37,539
A real bum.

145
00:16:38,457 --> 00:16:41,543
He is a bum! Did you see
who he sent to get us?.

146
00:16:42,544 --> 00:16:44,505
If that guy's the boss here,

147
00:16:44,588 --> 00:16:46,548
then here we can be the bosses.

148
00:16:48,383 --> 00:16:51,470
If a guy like him is boss here,
this area is ours!

149
00:16:52,429 --> 00:16:54,389
I'll live for 30 years
if he's boss here.

150
00:16:55,557 --> 00:16:58,393
Sure, because he's a retard!

151
00:16:58,560 --> 00:17:02,481
Get it?. I'll live for 30 years.

152
00:17:02,606 --> 00:17:05,359
But he could at least shave!

153
00:17:05,442 --> 00:17:06,527
Shave!

154
00:17:07,486 --> 00:17:09,446
"I'll smash your face!"

155
00:17:10,405 --> 00:17:12,533
Let's go have a snort to spite him.

156
00:17:13,450 --> 00:17:16,411
We've got everything,
we can do like we want.

157
00:17:19,581 --> 00:17:22,417
Anyway, he's a fat shit-ass.

158
00:17:22,584 --> 00:17:24,461
He bugged you?.

159
00:17:24,545 --> 00:17:26,547
He showers once a week!

160
00:17:30,551 --> 00:17:32,511
"I'll blow your heads off! "

161
00:17:56,577 --> 00:17:57,619
Roberto!

162
00:18:07,462 --> 00:18:09,423
Let's go, it's too small.

163
00:18:09,548 --> 00:18:13,427
- But the methane one's big.
- No, it's small.

164
00:18:13,594 --> 00:18:17,556
- Can I finish measuring?.
- No, we're wasting time.

165
00:18:20,559 --> 00:18:24,438
- I have to take some shots.
- What a bore with these pictures!

166
00:18:24,563 --> 00:18:26,398
Let's go!

167
00:18:31,612 --> 00:18:33,447
Just look at this.

168
00:18:34,531 --> 00:18:36,408
It's disgusting down there.

169
00:18:45,375 --> 00:18:46,543
Here is perfect.

170
00:18:47,544 --> 00:18:49,379
It's perfect.

171
00:18:49,546 --> 00:18:52,591
We're near the highway,
the trucks can get really close,

172
00:18:53,425 --> 00:18:56,386
they dump the earth
and cover all the water.

173
00:18:56,553 --> 00:18:57,554
Perfect.

174
00:18:59,598 --> 00:19:01,600
Franco, it's 85 meters.

175
00:19:02,434 --> 00:19:04,353
Get the length too.

176
00:19:06,522 --> 00:19:08,398
Come here.

177
00:19:11,360 --> 00:19:12,402
Dante.

178
00:19:12,528 --> 00:19:14,488
Hello, everything okay?.

179
00:19:16,615 --> 00:19:18,575
This is Roberto.

180
00:19:21,453 --> 00:19:24,581
- It's time we made room for youth.
- We need new energy.

181
00:19:24,623 --> 00:19:26,583
Take a few more shots.

182
00:19:28,502 --> 00:19:30,462
Did you hear?.

183
00:19:30,546 --> 00:19:32,548
They bombed me,

184
00:19:32,631 --> 00:19:34,508
at the cement plant.

185
00:19:35,634 --> 00:19:37,594
A whole wall came down,

186
00:19:38,428 --> 00:19:39,471
slowly.

187
00:19:39,638 --> 00:19:41,515
Be careful.

188
00:19:41,598 --> 00:19:43,517
Zio resolved it.

189
00:19:44,393 --> 00:19:47,396
I'd forgotten to pay
for some land I'd bought.

190
00:19:47,521 --> 00:19:50,440
- An injunction against payment?.
- Yeah!

191
00:19:50,566 --> 00:19:52,609
- What do you think?.
- It's fine.

192
00:19:53,443 --> 00:19:57,447
- Can we fill this quarry?.
- Sure can.

193
00:19:57,531 --> 00:19:59,491
Tell Zio it's fine.

194
00:19:59,575 --> 00:20:03,537
Remember, everything clean:
terracing, solid stuff...

195
00:20:04,538 --> 00:20:07,541
Or the redevelopment agency
will break our balls.

196
00:20:08,417 --> 00:20:11,587
Don't worry,
you emptied it and I'll fill it.

197
00:20:20,637 --> 00:20:24,516
All the pieces have to be cut
and the sizes worked out.

198
00:20:26,518 --> 00:20:28,478
They want 120 of these.

199
00:20:40,532 --> 00:20:42,534
Six and seven are identical.

200
00:20:46,497 --> 00:20:48,540
Here the satin is cut on the bias.

201
00:20:48,624 --> 00:20:50,542
It's all hand-hemmed.

202
00:20:50,626 --> 00:20:52,503
Is it tough?.

203
00:20:52,586 --> 00:20:55,547
The models aren't hard,
I can do it.

204
00:20:58,425 --> 00:21:00,636
Eight hundred items in two months,
is our request.

205
00:21:01,428 --> 00:21:04,389
Keep in mind
we start at 50 euros per item.

206
00:21:05,557 --> 00:21:08,519
You've seen the models,
the price is good,

207
00:21:08,644 --> 00:21:11,438
estimate and make your offers.

208
00:21:12,606 --> 00:21:14,608
Thirty euro, 30 days?.

209
00:21:15,442 --> 00:21:17,402
Don't go any lower.

210
00:21:17,528 --> 00:21:19,530
This is high fashion,
it's not pret-a-porter.

211
00:21:19,571 --> 00:21:21,532
Forty-five, in two months.

212
00:21:23,492 --> 00:21:25,536
- Ms. Zamarion!
- Yes?.

213
00:21:25,619 --> 00:21:27,621
Thirty-eight, forty.

214
00:21:28,413 --> 00:21:30,457
That's a very interesting proposal.

215
00:21:30,541 --> 00:21:32,459
Thirty-five, thirty-five,

216
00:21:32,543 --> 00:21:35,504
excellent workmanship
and delivery times respected.

217
00:21:36,630 --> 00:21:38,549
Thirty, thirty!

218
00:21:46,390 --> 00:21:47,558
Please,

219
00:21:47,641 --> 00:21:50,394
we're not imposing anything!

220
00:21:51,436 --> 00:21:53,480
Did we say thirty, thirty?.

221
00:21:54,606 --> 00:21:56,483
At this point

222
00:21:56,608 --> 00:21:58,485
twenty-eight, thirty!

223
00:22:02,531 --> 00:22:04,449
Thirty, twenty-five!

224
00:22:06,451 --> 00:22:08,495
I can't lose this bid.

225
00:22:09,621 --> 00:22:11,623
Come here, there's some bubbly!

226
00:22:14,501 --> 00:22:16,420
Are they coming?.

227
00:22:16,503 --> 00:22:18,630
- I don't think so.
- Why not?.

228
00:22:21,550 --> 00:22:24,386
Five days less for delivery,

229
00:22:24,469 --> 00:22:27,389
we'll have to work overtime,
and I'll do nights...

230
00:22:27,472 --> 00:22:29,474
What's odd about that?.

231
00:22:29,558 --> 00:22:31,518
They're talking overtime pay.

232
00:22:31,602 --> 00:22:33,562
They'll get it!

233
00:22:33,604 --> 00:22:36,565
Am I scared of a little overtime?.

234
00:22:38,525 --> 00:22:40,444
Like the last time?.

235
00:22:40,485 --> 00:22:42,529
Don't worry,
this time it's a sure thing.

236
00:22:45,616 --> 00:22:48,494
- They've lost their trust.
- I know.

237
00:22:48,577 --> 00:22:52,498
- I asked you to talk to them.
- You do it, please.

238
00:22:52,581 --> 00:22:55,542
You're on closer terms,
they respect you.

239
00:22:56,543 --> 00:22:58,504
Do me this favor.

240
00:22:59,588 --> 00:23:01,590
Don't say no, go talk to them.

241
00:23:02,633 --> 00:23:04,551
You know I'm fond of you,

242
00:23:04,635 --> 00:23:06,595
I'll have to make
a gold statue to you!

243
00:23:06,637 --> 00:23:09,431
I'll go down and see the accountant
for the money.

244
00:23:14,603 --> 00:23:17,439
Sorry, how much is this?.

245
00:23:18,398 --> 00:23:19,525
Ten thousand.

246
00:23:21,485 --> 00:23:23,529
It's not enough, I need more.

247
00:23:24,446 --> 00:23:25,572
Twice that at least.

248
00:23:26,406 --> 00:23:28,450
Mr. Enzo,
you're already "complicated".

249
00:23:28,534 --> 00:23:30,536
Yes, but for personal affairs.

250
00:23:30,619 --> 00:23:33,455
I need this for work.

251
00:23:33,539 --> 00:23:35,541
I'll give it back in three months.

252
00:23:35,624 --> 00:23:38,418
But this isn't enough.

253
00:23:38,502 --> 00:23:40,587
If you don't need it
and it's not enough,

254
00:23:41,463 --> 00:23:42,589
I'll take it back.

255
00:23:43,423 --> 00:23:44,550
It's best for you.

256
00:23:45,384 --> 00:23:47,469
Don't be like that, listen,

257
00:23:47,553 --> 00:23:49,596
I need at least double!

258
00:23:50,514 --> 00:23:52,391
It's no risk,

259
00:23:52,474 --> 00:23:53,600
you'll earn from it, right?.

260
00:23:54,434 --> 00:23:55,519
What can I say?.

261
00:23:55,602 --> 00:23:58,438
I'll pass it on,
can you make-do for now?.

262
00:23:58,564 --> 00:24:00,524
Yes, I'll take it.

263
00:24:11,493 --> 00:24:13,453
Congratulations, Mr. Pasquale.

264
00:24:13,537 --> 00:24:14,580
Thank you.

265
00:24:15,414 --> 00:24:16,582
We met yesterday.

266
00:24:18,417 --> 00:24:20,544
I need your help.

267
00:24:27,551 --> 00:24:29,595
I am having trouble with work.

268
00:24:31,638 --> 00:24:34,558
I have to get into
haute couture right away,

269
00:24:36,518 --> 00:24:38,478
but for me

270
00:24:39,438 --> 00:24:41,440
it is very difficult.

271
00:24:41,481 --> 00:24:43,525
I need help.

